text: SSSOR-Metalurh Zaporizhia is a Ukrainian football team based in Zaporizhia, Ukraine. The club has been featured regularly in the Ukrainian Second Division it serves as a junior team for the FC Metalurh Zaporizhia franchise. Like most tributary teams, the best players are sent up to the senior team, meanwhile developing other players for further call-ups. Among notable players was Vasyl Storchak.
